caption.title: Viral titers obtained from positive bodies, heads and saliva according to the DENV serotype/genotype strain.
caption.p: (A) Body infection titer, (B) head infection titer and (C) saliva infection titer at 14 days post-infection. Median and interquartile range are shown for each viral strain. Significant differences are indicated by asterisks (Two-sample Wilcoxon test; * p< 0.05; ** p< 0.01; *** p< 0.001).
